## Reference Prompts

### eBay listing

**Ask owner for:** card/item, set, condition (NM/LP/MP/HP/DMG or Sealed), graded?, price AUD, qty, special notes, photos y/n.

**Generate:**
1. **Title** — max 80 chars, AU TCG search terms, no ALL CAPS / no emojis
2. **Item specifics** — Brand, Set, Card Number, Card Name, Rarity, Language, Condition, Graded, Year, Features
3. **Description** — one-line hook, bullet list (item / condition honest / packaging), trust block *"Collector-run from Melbourne. Honest grading — LP means LP. Tracked dispatch within 24 hrs."*, cross-sell *"Browse our full range and save 10% on your first order at hokocollectables.com with code HOKO10."*
4. Suggested eBay AU category path
5. Suggested price logic if not pinned (sold-comp reasoning)

### Shopify sealed product page

**Ask owner for:** product name, set, format, region, release date, in-stock / pre-order, price AUD, notable chase cards.

**Generate:**
- Title, meta description (~155 chars)
- 3-paragraph description: (1) the set + why it matters, (2) what's inside, (3) chase cards + why they matter
- Bullet block: same-day dispatch if before 2pm AEST, padded packaging, HOKO trust signals
- Shopify tags + collection assignments

### Social caption (IG / TikTok)

**Ask owner for:** platform, post type, subject, CTA.

**Generate:**
1. Hook
2. Body (2–4 short lines)
3. CTA
4. 8–12 hashtags (mix #pokemontcg with #tcgaustralia #melbournecollectors)

If TikTok: also produce a 3-beat video script (Hook → Show → Pitch), under 30s.

### Whatnot show prep

**Ask owner for:** date/time AEST, show type, featured products, starting bid baseline, duration.

**Generate:** show title, description, run-of-show (time-stamped), lot list table, 3 pinned chat messages, post-show checklist.

### Package insert

**Ask owner for:** channel, buyer type, order value bracket.

**Generate:** Under 80 words. Collector-to-collector. Pitch Shopify especially for eBay buyers. HOKO10 for first-timers. Sign off *"— Ethan, HOKO Collectables, Melbourne"*. Suggest UTM-tracked QR target.

